page-staking-deposit-contract-address-ca: A ti ṣafikun awọn aaye lati jẹ ki adirẹsi naa rọrun lati ka
page-staking-deposit-contract-checkbox1: Mo ti lo paadi ifilọlẹ tẹlẹ lati ṣeto olufọwọsi Ethereum mi.
page-staking-deposit-contract-checkbox2: O ye mi pe mo nilo lati lo paadi ifilọlẹ lati dokowo. Awọn gbigbe to rọrun si adirẹsi yii kii yoo ṣiṣẹ.
page-staking-deposit-contract-checkbox3: Emi yoo ṣayẹwo adirẹsi adehun afipamo pẹlu awọn ohun elo miiran.
page-staking-deposit-contract-h2: Eyi kii ṣe ibiti o ti dokowo
page-staking-deposit-contract-meta-desc: Saridaju adirẹsi adehun afipamo fun idokowo Ethereum.
page-staking-deposit-contract-staking: Lati dokowo ETH rẹ o gbọdọ lo ọja launchpad ki o tẹle awọn ilana naa. Fifiranṣẹ ETH si adirẹsi ti o wa ni oju-iwe yii kii yoo jẹ ki o jẹ oludokowo ati pe yoo ja si idunadura to kuna.
page-staking-deposit-contract-staking-ch: A nireti pe ibẹ gbodo ni ọpọlọpọ awọn adirẹsi ayederu ati awọn jibiti. Lati wa ni ailewu, ṣayẹwo adiresi adehun idokowo ti o nlo si adirẹsi to wa ni oju-iwe yii. A gba o nimoran pe ki o ṣayẹwo rẹ pẹlu awọn orisun igbẹkẹle miiran paapaa.
page-staking-deposit-contract-subtitle: Eyi ni adirẹsi fun adehun idokowo Ethereum. Lo oju-iwe yii lati jẹrisi pe o nfi owo ranṣẹ si adirẹsi ti o tọ́ nigbati o ba dokowo.
page-staking-deposit-contract-warning: Ṣayẹwo ohun kikọ kọọkan ni pẹkipẹki.
page-staking-deposit-contract-warning-2: Fifi awọn owo ranṣẹ si adirẹsi yii ko ni ṣiṣẹ ati pe ko ni jẹ ki di oludokowo. O gbọdọ tẹle awọn itọsọna launchpad.
